    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! \ud83c\udf1f This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and meticulously cared for. It seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 48500.0,
